      },
      "type": "term",
      "surface": {
        "jp": "無線LAN",
        "zh": "无线LAN",
        "en": "Wireless LAN"
      },
      "definition": {
        "jp": "無線でコンピュータ同士をつなぐLANです。Wi-Fi（Wireless Fidelity）とほぼ同じ意味ですが、厳密には、Wi-Fiは無線LAN機器が相互接続できることを示すブランド名です。",
        "zh": "通过无线方式连接计算机之间的LAN。与Wi-Fi（Wireless Fidelity）含义基本相同，但严格来说，Wi-Fi是表示无线LAN设备之间可以相互连接的品牌名称。",
        "en": "A LAN that connects computers wirelessly. It has almost the same meaning as Wi-Fi (Wireless Fidelity), but strictly speaking, Wi-Fi is a brand name indicating that wireless LAN devices can interconnect with each other."
      },
      "kana_helper": null
    },
    {
      "id": "itpassport_r6::term::p479::2",
      "anchor": {
        "page": 479,
        "block_id": "page_479_block_2",
        "section_path": []
      },
      "type": "term",
      "surface": {
        "jp": "アクセスポイント",
        "zh": "接入点",
        "en": "Access Point"
      },
      "definition": {
        "jp": "コンピュータを無線LANに接続するための機器です。みなさんの家庭では、ルーターがアクセスポイントの役割をしていることが多いです。",
        "zh": "用于将计算机连接到无线LAN的设备。在大家的家庭中，路由器通常承担着接入点的角色。",
        "en": "A device used to connect computers to a wireless LAN. In most households, the router serves as the access point."
      },
      "kana_helper": {
        "surface": "アクセスポイント",
        "reading": "akusesu pointo",
        "zh_concept": "接入点",
        "auto_backfill": false
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "itpassport_r6::term::p479::3",
      "anchor": {
        "page": 479,
        "block_id": "page_479_block_3",
        "section_path": []
      },
      "type": "term",
      "surface": {
        "jp": "ESSID（Extended Service Set IDentifier）",
        "zh": "扩展服务集标识符（ESSID）",
        "en": "ESSID (Extended Service Set IDentifier)"
      },
      "definition": {
        "jp": "無線LANにおけるネットワークの名前です。ITパスポート試験では「無線LANのネットワークを識別する文字列」という文章で出題されることもあります。ESSIDは「アクセスポイントを識別するための名前」ともいえます。",
        "zh": "无线LAN中网络的名称。在IT护照考试中，有时会以\"用于识别无线LAN网络的字符串\"这样的表述出题。ESSID也可以说是\"用于识别接入点的名称\"。",
        "en": "The name of a network in a wireless LAN. On the IT Passport exam, it is sometimes phrased as \"a character string that identifies a wireless LAN network.\" ESSID can also be described as \"a name for identifying an access point.\""
      },
      "kana_helper": null
    },
